        <mxCell id="legend" value="&lt;b&gt;Legend:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;🟥 Red = operatori K8s-native (ECK, Keycloak Op)&lt;br&gt;🟧 Orange = gateway / edge (nginx, Kong, Dynu, server)&lt;br&gt;🟪 Purple = observability (Prometheus, Grafana)&lt;br&gt;🟩 Green = messaging (Strimzi, Kafka)&lt;br&gt;🟨 Yellow = data persistent&amp;#259; (CNPG, MOCO, Mongo)&lt;br&gt;🟦 Blue = cluster / system / business&lt;br&gt;🟦 Teal = Crossplane (control-plane declarativ)&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Linie continu&amp;#259;&lt;/b&gt; = sincronizat • &lt;b&gt;linie punctat&amp;#259;&lt;/b&gt; = orphan / de f&amp;#259;cut&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10px&quot;&gt;Wave &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9px;background:#fff;padding:1px 4px;border:1px solid #999;border-radius:3px&quot;&gt;W&amp;lt;n&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; = argocd.argoproj.io/sync-wave.&lt;/span&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#999;rounded=1;spacing=8;fontSize=11;" vertex="1" parent="1">
